title: Sunlounger - Another Day On The Terrace - 2CD - 2007 [FLAC]
description:
This CD case is destined to sit empty once you get Sunlounger on your
stereo itll be staying there Packed with gorgeous Balearic chill-out tracks
and pumping peak-time grooves, its got something for whatever time of
day or night you happen to be awake.
Crafted by Roger-Pierre Shah, the man revered as one of the hottest
names of the moment by the press, itll have you booking yourflight to the
White Island for a slice of the action.
Roger got his first deal in 1995, but hes come a long way from those
firstcheap commercial records to grab the attention of Armada Music.

Roger is on a mission to produce the most beautiful Balearic tunesin
the world, so mix yourself a vodka-lemon and tune in
www.armadamusic.nl
